\c 53
\s Vanhu vese vakashata
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. NeMaharati. Masikiri. \add Pisarema\add* raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Benzi rakati mumoyo maro: Hakuna Mwari. Vakaodza, vakaita uipi hunonyangadza; hakuna anoita zvakanaka.
\v 2 Mwari wakatarisa pasi ari kumatenga pamusoro pevanakomana vevanhu, kuona kana pane anonzwisisa, anotsvaka Mwari.
\v 3 Umwe neumwe wavo wakadzokera shure; vakasvibiswa pamwe chete; hakuna anoita zvakanaka, hakuna neumwe.
\v 4 Vaiti vezvakaipa havana zivo here? Avo vanodya vanhu vangu \add se\add*vanodya chingwa. Havadani Mwari.
\v 5 Ipapo vaitya zvekutya, pasina chinotyisa; nokuti Mwari wakaparadzira mapfupa eanokudzikirai musasa; maka\add va\add*nyadzisa; nokuti Mwari wakavazvidza.
\p
\v 6 Dai ruponeso rukuru rwaIsraeri rwaibva paZiyoni! Mwari paanodzosa utapwa hwevanhu vake, Jakove achafara, Israeri achapembera.